HEADWORD: Plano-convex
<hw>Pla"no-con"vex</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Plano-</ets> + <ets>convex</ets>.]</ety> <def>Plane or flat
on one side, and convex on the other; <as>as, a <ex>plano-convex</ex>
lens</as>. See <er>Convex</er>, and <er>Lens</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

